you can just roll up to the top

00:21:57.583 --> 00:21:59.490
of the hill and escape.
 

00:21:59.490 --> 00:22:01.480
That's classical mechanics.
 

00:22:01.480 --> 00:22:05.011
Now we want to ask ourselves,
