00:22:05.011 --> 00:22:06.990
what does the particle do?
 

00:22:06.990 --> 00:22:10.788
That's our goal.
 

00:22:10.788 --> 00:22:14.076
So I'm going to take a
following simpler problem,

00:22:14.076 --> 00:22:16.608
because it's mathematically
easier.

00:22:16.608 --> 00:22:20.618
