00:22:38.640 --> 00:22:43.568
My fake potential has got sharp
corners.

00:22:43.568 --> 00:22:46.673
I want to take a particle of
some energy and ask,

00:22:46.673 --> 00:22:49.779
what are the allowed energies
in this problem?

00:22:49.779 --> 00:22:51.920
What do the corresponding
functions look like?

00:22:51.920 --> 00:22:55.740
That's what we're asking.
 

00:22:55.740 --> 00:22:58.996
So the rule is to go back to
