00:48:25.699 --> 00:48:26.750
So everyone with me?
 

00:48:26.750 --> 00:48:30.617
This is like knowing the
spectrum of this artificial

00:48:30.617 --> 00:48:31.150
atom.
 

00:48:31.150 --> 00:48:34.210
In a real atom,
the electron is forced to stay

00:48:34.210 --> 00:48:36.733
near the nucleus,
because the 1 over r

00:48:36.733 --> 00:48:39.101
potential,
if you plot it as a function of

00:48:39.101 --> 00:48:41.409
r,
looks like a well.

00:48:41.409 --> 00:48:44.750
And the particle is somewhere
here.

00:48:44.750 --> 00:48:50.771
In this problem,
the particle is confined by the

00:48:50.771 --> 00:48:51.539
box.
 

00:48:51.539 --> 00:48:54.503
Whenever you have a confining
thing that keeps the particle in

00:48:54.503 --> 00:48:56.739
a certain region,
the energy gets quantized.

00:48:56.739 --> 00:49:00.396
And we found out in our first
example the quantized energy

00:49:00.396 --> 00:49:02.449
levels of a particle in a box.
 

00:49:02.449 --> 00:49:05.871
And you can probe the particle
by shining light and the energy

00:49:05.871 --> 00:49:07.610
levels are plotted like this.
 

00:49:07.610 --> 00:49:10.769
This is n=1,
this is n=2,

00:49:10.769 --> 00:49:12.599
which is n=3.
 

00:49:12.599 --> 00:49:15.610
