00:49:23.099 --> 00:49:25.219
Energy grows like n^(2).
 

00:49:25.219 --> 00:49:28.262
And then you can come from
there to there emitting a

00:49:28.262 --> 00:49:29.786
photon,
or you can go from there to

00:49:29.786 --> 00:49:32.199
there emitting a photon,
or you can go from here to here

00:49:32.199 --> 00:49:33.179
absorbing a photon.
 

00:49:33.179 --> 00:49:35.349
You can do all kinds of things.
 

00:49:35.349 --> 00:49:38.119
That's how if you want you can
test quantum mechanics.

00:49:38.119 --> 00:49:41.688
Put a known particle inside the
